ay from Thailand to take part in our project. They were completely blown away by the venue and the overall styling. In a spur of a moment they’ve decided to get married for real, in a commitment ceremony carried out by a local priest. It was a challenge to find a celebrant with 2 hour notice, especially in high wedding season, but it was just meant to be.\nIt was an emotional moment to watch Magda & Alex tie the knot. With no time to prepare vows, we knew their words came from their hearts. Their commitment was the most romantic wedding we’ve all ever witnessed.\nHere is a small selection of photos from this amazing day.","cover":"http://images.bridestory.com/image/upload/assets/111_Bali_bugprp.jpg","createdAt":"2017-02-19T04:44:41+00:00","updatedAt":"2017-02-19T14:26:24+00:00","status":"published","externalId":null,"location":"Bali","vendorId":"811104","isHilda":false,"views":290,"category":{"data":{"id":56,"name":"Wedding Planner","slug":"wedding-planning","description":"Berurusan dengan tekanan dan stres saat mempersiapkan pernikahan itu bukan masalah Anda. Fokus utama Anda adalah menyiapkan rencana utama yang akan mencakup semua aspek pernikahan, dari pembiayaan sampai menangani vendor.","createdAt":"-0001-11-30T00:00:00+00:00","updatedAt":"2015-10-20T09:44:41+00:00","imageUrl":"http://images.bridestory.com/image/upload/banner/categories/Wedding-Organizer.jpg"}}}}}}},"89033":{"id":89033,"type":"work","qualityContent":"0","cultural":"0","work":{"data":{"id":7002277,"name":"TV528610.jpg1488184106718","description":"","type":"image","slug":"","projectId":"917420","width":"1224","height":"816","vendorId":811129,"isHilda":false,"imageType":"image/jpg","imageUrl":"http://images.bridestory.com/image/upload/assets/TV528610_qtb60v.jpg","videoUrl":null,"orientation":"landscape","votes":"7","vendor":{"data":{"id":811129,"accountId":405382,"businessName":"Tonny Valenzio Photo","slug":"tonny-valenzio-photo","isDiamond":0,"isHilda":false,"isFollowBridestory":0,"status":1,"cre